Megatron steps in, "Skullgrin, clear the way in tank mode. Astroblast,
full steam ahead" Megatron says. He loved it when his plans came
together.


Motormaster kept flying up, and then towards Surgital. "Surgital, we
will need your help" he says, he then takes aim, and fires at the hole
Greven's in.

Speedbreaker also gets into Astoblast, and gets his gun ready.
